item.title: AYURVEDA LOUNGE 1
item.description: Follow up from the Twilight Sleeper collective, this mix is more orientated to the funk/hip-trip hop listener. Opening duties by Colourbox and De La Soul remix by Tribe Called Quest, slowly breaking into the dark sensual sound of De Phazz with the subtle hints of dub reggae. Enjoy, and peace out..
